Sources: Amazon will require some remote corporate employees to relocate as part of a mandate requiring workers to be in the office three days a week
A look at Samsung's $17B and Texas Instruments' $30B chip fabs in Texas, as the state becomes a US chipmaking hub with six projects expected to create 8K+ jobs
